---
<BaseLayout
  title="Verbatim Voice Dictation for Healthcare Teams: A Practical Guide"
  description="Verbatim voice dictation for healthcare teams — doctors, nurses, allied health, pharmacy, and clinical administrators. No AI generation. No data stored. Free 30-day Medical trial."
  extraSchema={extraSchema}
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container m-hero-split">
      <div class="m-hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">FOR HEALTHCARE TEAMS</p>
        <h1 class="m-h1">Verbatim Voice Dictation for Healthcare Teams: A Practical Guide</h1>
        <p class="m-lead">What you say is what appears — verbatim, every time. No AI generation, no hallucinations, no data stored, no compliance headaches. Speech Recognition Cloud Medical works in any Windows clinical or practice system. Free 30-day trial above.</p>
        <div class="m-cta-row">
          <a href="#trial" class="btn-primary">Start free 30-day Medical trial</a>
          <a href="#quickstart" class="btn-secondary">Jump to quick start</a>
        </div>
